<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Product</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../public/style/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 

    This file contains the HTML and embedded JavaScript (EJS) code for the "Add Product" page in the admin section of the web shop.

    Components:
    1. Navbar:
        - A navigation bar with links to different sections of the web shop (Products, Cart, Add Product, Admin).
        - The "Add Product" link is marked as active.

    2. Container:
        - A container with a white text color that holds the main content of the page.

    3. Header:
        - A centered header with the title "Add Product".

    4. Product Add Form:
        - A form for adding a new product, with fields for title, description, price, and image URL.
        - The form uses the POST method to submit data to the "/add-product" endpoint.
        - Each input field is wrapped in a form-group div for styling purposes.
        - The form includes a submit button with the label "Add Product".

    Styling:
    - The page uses Bootstrap classes for styling, including navbar-dark, bg-dark, container-fluid, text-white, form-control, and btn-success.
    - The form container has additional padding, background color, and rounded corners for better visual presentation.
    -->
    
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">E-Pood</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/">Products</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/cart">Cart</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="/add-product">Add Product</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/admin">Admin</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container text-white">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h1 class="text-center">Add Product</h1>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12">

                <div class="product-add-container p-2 bg-dark rounded text-white">
                    <form action="/add-product" method="POST">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label for="title" class="form-label">Title</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="title" name="title">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label for="description" class="form-label">Description</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" id="description" name="description"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label for="price" class="form-label">Price</label>
                            <input type="number" class="form-control" id="price" name="price">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label for="image" class="form-label">Image</label>
                            <input type="text" placeholder="Palun sisesta LINK!"  class="form-control" id="image" name="image">
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success p-2">Add Product</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>